description:

Two changes have been applied to the TeX-templates project:

1. The project structure is refactored for clearly separatin the LaTeX source code (in `tex/` folder) and the documentation files (in `doc/` folder).
2. The documentation of `utbmciadreport` is fixed and the errors inside have been removed.

